      "rationale": "Validation experiments use the same FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry, same blood analogue fluid, same operating envelope (2–6 L/min, 2500–3500 RPM), and same hemolysis measurement protocol as the COU. Geometric and operational similarity index > 0.95. No extrapolation beyond validated operating range required. Achieved level 3 meets required level 3."
